data.description: This elegant single family home sits on a quiet street near several outdoor facilitys such as Anclote Gulf Park under 3 miles away, and Key Vista Park barely over 1.5 miles away and is conveniently located in beautiful Beacon Square. Just minutes away is Anclote High School as well as Gulf Trace Elementary School. A community pool and shuffleboard are also available. Upon entrance of this stunning home, you are warmly greeted by new floors, fresh paint, and a bright and open floor plan seamlessly connecting the kitchen to the living room and leading to the inviting, sunny backyard. Meticulous attention to detail is presented in the kitchen with new granite counter tops, customized backsplash, new dark cherry cabinets, and brand-name stainless steel appliances included with the house such as refrigerator, oven and stovetop, range hood, garbage disposal, dish washer . Adjacent to the living room, there’s a comfortable family room and an oversized master bedroom with a sitting area and bonus room for a walk-in closet, office, or storage room. It has 4 bedrooms and a garage converted to large extra living space.
